\f2 Assignment: 
\f1 \uc0\u8232 
\f2 1) Use the "loopSampler" SynthDef from this week's IV_Sampling.rtf file to play back your own soundfile with both downsampling and upsampling, and with moveable, bidirectional loops. Then, write a Routine that plays that SynthDef while changing the different parameters (pitch, start, and end points) each time it plays. Record one minute of your sampling piece to bring to class next week. 
\fs32 \

